# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:12
translate chinese gertrude7_e4a486c5:

    # "I start talking with Gertrude about the things that have been on my mind the last few days, but very quickly notice that she's not paying attention."
    "我开始跟格特鲁德聊起这几天萦绕在心头的事，但很快发现她心不在焉。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:13
translate chinese gertrude7_97b63e7d:

    # "She seems upset about something."
    "她好像因为什么事很不开心。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:14
translate chinese gertrude7_aae39d82:

    # pc "Hey, Gertrude? You okay?"
    pc "嘿，格特鲁德？你还好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:16
translate chinese gertrude7_efec7b50:

    # sc "Sorry, what? I kind of blanked out for a while there."
    sc "抱歉，你说什么？我刚才有点走神。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:17
translate chinese gertrude7_482afb8f:

    # pc "Yeah, I noticed. What's going on?"
    pc "是啊，我注意到了。怎么了？"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:19
translate chinese gertrude7_cec5b723:

    # sc "It's just been a bad day."
    sc "今天就是过得不太顺。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:20
translate chinese gertrude7_e262f6a2:

    # pc "But the day has just started."
    pc "但这天才刚开始啊。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:21
translate chinese gertrude7_f0bbe887:

    # sc "Yeah, well yesterday was bad too. And the day before. And probably the day before that."
    sc "是啊，不过昨天也不太好。大前天也是。大概大前天之前也是。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:22
translate chinese gertrude7_7ce1ef4f:

    # pc "Sounds rough. Want to talk about it?"
    pc "听起来挺难熬的。想聊聊吗？"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:23
translate chinese gertrude7_f2ba9b25:

    # sc "I probably shouldn't."
    sc "我可能不该说。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:24
translate chinese gertrude7_9a6b5393:

    # pc "It's okay. We're friends, remember?"
    pc "没关系。我们是朋友，记得吗？"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:26
translate chinese gertrude7_a064582c:

    # sc "Yeah, I guess we are."
    sc "是啊，我想我们确实是。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:28
translate chinese gertrude7_c6b054d3:

    # sc "Okay, so my husband is a VP at his company and he has to go away for weeks sometimes. I think we've talked about this before."
    sc "好吧，我丈夫是公司副总裁，有时得出差好几周。我觉得我们之前聊过这个。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:29
translate chinese gertrude7_abe3824b:

    # pc "Yeah, I remember."
    pc "是啊，我记得。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:30
translate chinese gertrude7_d8c01a95:

    # sc "Well he's been away for two weeks right now. He was supposed to come back today, but he called this morning and told me he was going to be gone another week."
    sc "他现在已经出差两周了。本来今天该回来的，但他今早打电话说还要再走一周。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:31
translate chinese gertrude7_f97068f9:

    # pc "Three weeks… that's rough."
    pc "三周……真够呛。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:33
translate chinese gertrude7_114695f1:

    # sc "What's worse is I think I heard another voice in the background when I was talking to him. A woman's voice. Whispering."
    sc "更糟的是，我跟他说话的时候，好像听到背景里还有另一个声音。女人的声音。在低语。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:34
translate chinese gertrude7_78bd9374:

    # pc "Maybe he was just around other people?"
    pc "也许他只是和别人在一起？"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:35
translate chinese gertrude7_d199aa10:

    # sc "He told me he was in his hotel room."
    sc "他说他在酒店房间里。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:36
translate chinese gertrude7_f8a26f59:

    # pc "Oof. Maybe it was just the TV?"
    pc "哎哟。也许只是电视里的声音？"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:38
translate chinese gertrude7_c1291f74:

    # sc "Maybe. But I've had a feeling he's been cheating on me for a while. This is just another thing to add to that suspicion."
    sc "也许吧。但我总觉得他已经背着我出轨有一阵子了。这只是让我更加怀疑的又一个证据。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:39
translate chinese gertrude7_df2e8061:

    # pc "Sorry, Gertrude."
    pc "抱歉，格特鲁德。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:41
translate chinese gertrude7_bb8360c8:

    # sc "Yeah. I'm not sure what to do."
    sc "是啊。我真不知道该怎么办。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:43
translate chinese gertrude7_124214fb:

    # sc "Maybe I'll just find myself a college guy and cheat on him right back."
    sc "也许我就找个大学生，然后也背着他出轨。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:47
translate chinese gertrude7_a472e7bd:

    # sc "I bet you would!"
    sc "我敢打赌你会这么做！"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:48
translate chinese gertrude7_9155355e:

    # sc "You're kind of a player, aren't you?"
    sc "你这人挺花心的，对吧？"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:49
translate chinese gertrude7_64b00869:

    # pc "I'm just trying to help you out here."
    pc "我只是想帮你出出主意。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:50
translate chinese gertrude7_e344197a:

    # sc "Yeah, sure you are."
    sc "是啊，你肯定是在帮我。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:52
translate chinese gertrude7_dee19707:

    # sc "Oh, thanks for that. I needed a laugh."
    sc "哦，谢谢你。我正需要笑一笑。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:55
translate chinese gertrude7_1d5aeafb:

    # sc "Thanks, [pcname]."
    sc "谢谢，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:57
translate chinese gertrude7_09c5f7bb:

    # sc "I shouldn't though. Two wrongs don't make a right, you know."
    sc "不过我真不该这么做。你知道的，以牙还牙，错上加错。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:58
translate chinese gertrude7_990441d4:

    # pc "Yeah. But sometimes, even if it's wrong, it feels right."
    pc "是啊。但有时候，哪怕是错的，感觉却对。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:60
translate chinese gertrude7_94da6d28:

    # sc "Yeah, I guess it does."
    sc "是啊，我想确实如此。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:63
translate chinese gertrude7_a0094ffa:

    # sc "Yeah, you're probably right."
    sc "是啊，你大概说得对。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:64
translate chinese gertrude7_2caddb85:

    # sc "Two wrongs don't make a right, as my mother always said."
    sc "错上加错，就像我妈妈常说的。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:65
translate chinese gertrude7_14520e38:

    # sc "Even though sometimes doing wrong things feels right."
    sc "尽管有时候做错事的感觉却很对。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:67
translate chinese gertrude7_4e6348a3:

    # sc "Anyway, now that you've been my counselor for the morning, you better get to class."
    sc "不管怎样，既然你今天上午当了我的心理咨询师，你最好去上课了。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:68
translate chinese gertrude7_b1563ec7:

    # pc "Okay, I'll talk to you later."
    pc "好的，待会儿再聊。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:71
translate chinese gertrude7_98ca816f:

    # "We both stand up, very close to each other. Looking at each other."
    "我们俩都站了起来，彼此靠得很近。互相凝视着。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:74
translate chinese gertrude7_ac0b2138:

    # "I start to lean in to kiss her."
    "我开始俯身想吻她。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:77
translate chinese gertrude7_951013bf:

    # "But she quickly puts her hand on my shoulder and holds me back, pulling away from me."
    "但她迅速把手搭在我的肩膀上，把我拉住，然后从我身边退开。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:78
translate chinese gertrude7_2262058f:

    # sc "You should head to class, [pcname]."
    sc "你该去上课了，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:79
translate chinese gertrude7_877ec67b:

    # pc "Right. Sorry."
    pc "对。抱歉。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:80
translate chinese gertrude7_cfee34fc:

    # sc "It's okay. I'll see you later, okay?"
    sc "没关系。待会儿见，好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:81
translate chinese gertrude7_850ead77:

    # pc "Okay. Bye, Gertrude."
    pc "好的。再见，格特鲁德。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:85
translate chinese gertrude7_fe8a244e:

    # "I wrap my arms around her and pull her close."
    "我搂住她，把她拉近。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:86
translate chinese gertrude7_03e06438:

    # "At first, she is a little stiff, but she quickly relaxes and returns the hug, pressing herself against me."
    "起初她有些僵硬，但很快放松下来，回抱了我，紧贴着我。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:87
translate chinese gertrude7_b5efc9fe:

    # "We hold each other like that for a little longer than normal for a casual, friendly hug."
    "我们这样拥抱的时间，比平常随意的友好拥抱要长一些。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:88
translate chinese gertrude7_3abc9c1d:

    # "When I finally start to pull away, she lets go of me reluctantly."
    "当我终于开始松开时，她不情愿地放开了我。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:92
translate chinese gertrude7_8e28123b:

    # sc "Thanks for that, [pcname]. That was nice. But you better get to class."
    sc "谢谢你，[pcname]。这感觉真好。不过你最好去上课了。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:93
translate chinese gertrude7_1070058d:

    # pc "Yeah, okay. Bye, Gertrude."
    pc "嗯，好的。再见，格特鲁德。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:95
translate chinese gertrude7_0e8f1b03:

    # pc "Well, I better get to class."
    pc "是啊，我得去上课了。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:96
translate chinese gertrude7_5c60e9c3:

    # sc "Right. Okay, see you later, [pcname]."
    sc "对。好的，待会儿见，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:97
translate chinese gertrude7_6679f75b:

    # pc "Bye, Gertrude."
    pc "再见，格特鲁德。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:100
translate chinese gertrude7_d7e41755:

    # "I leave her office and head to class."
    "我离开她的办公室，前往教室。"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:2
